{"tid":2094693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北京外交專家：北京條約是正式的法律手續，俄羅斯有擁有海參崴的權力","createTime":"2020-07-05T00:29:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-05T17:25:49.000Z","uid":42884,"like":613,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"e588bb805022c787970e11315bf1435f4ecec9ec","tid":2094693,"uid":42884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T00:29:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Q-XjI3vU9rI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQ-XjI3vU9rI&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmoRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=d43ccce1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Q-XjI3vU9rI</a><br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以答答我。<br />\n1860年10月24日，大清割讓九龍畀英國。<br />\n1860年11月14日，大清連同海參崴割讓左約40平方公里嘅地方畀俄國。<br />\n<br />\n點解一個係中國不可分割嘅一部份？<br />\n另一個就可以永遠送俾俄羅斯呢？<br />\n<br />\n咁係因為<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">中國共產黨本身就係勾結外國勢力（蘇聯共產國際），分裂中華民國國土，顛覆中華民國政權嘅恐怖組織</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"cc03fd4236071a05b2a698276e47afa2925191bf","tid":2094693,"uid":324930,"like":27,"dislike":4,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T00:30:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WVGvoX2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWVGvoX2.jpg&h=c2f51375&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n======<br />\n黃channel撐得好辛苦，可以幫手subscribe嗎？<br />\n⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️⚠️<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cSVPPOHCOLc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcSVPPOHCOLc&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmoRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=5dfb40a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cSVPPOHCOLc</a>"},{"pid":"0fe0b32a9d461f5c11395a90c143d5ad83e9d58d","tid":2094693,"uid":260012,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T00:36:36.000Z","msg":"因為佢想咪做囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b38b7880f592f3e4fa130affcc38eef2306d98","tid":2094693,"uid":204929,"like":94,"dislike":0,"score":94,"citedBy":2,"replyTi